---
import Layout from '../../../site-layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="极客魔咒工作室 · GeekSpell Studio | Miragea" lang="zh">
  <main class="gs-page">
    <div class="gs-stars" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="gs-wrap">
      <header class="gs-topbar">
        <span>EX_Her · 宇宙 AI 工坊 · 科普线</span>
        <nav>
          <a href="/zh/">← Miragea 档案</a>
          ·
          <a href="/eliora/atelier/zh/">宇宙 AI 工坊</a>
          ·
          <a href="/en/geekspell/">EN</a>
          ·
          <a href="/ja/geekspell/">JA</a>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <section class="gs-hero">
        <div>
          <p class="gs-eyebrow">GSP / 极客魔咒 · E/X-04 Example × Execution</p>
          <h1>极客<em>魔咒</em>工作室</h1>
          <p class="gs-sub-en">GeekSpell Studio — Spells for the AI age</p>
          <p class="gs-lead">
            把 Prompt 写成中文创作者能听懂、能复现的咒语。不是玄学鸡汤，是带约束的极客魔法——
            与 Miragea 感知档案同源，由宇宙 AI 工坊播出。
          </p>
          <p class="gs-tag">在运行之前，先念对咒语。</p>
          <div class="gs-cta">
            <a class="gs-btn gs-btn-primary" href="https://space.bilibili.com/1321407655" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              >B站 · 极客魔咒</a
            >
            <a class="gs-btn gs-btn-ghost" href="/zh/geekspell/ep01-codex-language/">EP01 · Codex 语言</a>
            <a class="gs-btn gs-btn-ghost" href="/zh/geekspell/ep02-grok45/">EP02 · Grok 4.5</a>
            <a class="gs-btn gs-btn-ghost" href="/zh/geekspell/ep03-agent-command/">EP03 · Agent 命令</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <aside class="gs-panel" aria-label="示例咒语">
          <div class="gs-panel-label">⌁ SPELL_BLOCK · bilingual_pattern</div>
          <pre class="gs-spell"><span class="cm"># EN: technical spec (Codex / API)</span>
<span class="kw">TASK</span>: Refactor auth middleware
<span class="kw">OUTPUT</span>: unified diff only
<span class="kw">CONSTRAINTS</span>: no new deps; TypeScript strict

<span class="cm"># ZH: aesthetic + intent</span>
<span class="zh">风格</span>: Miragea 暗色宇宙感，金边玻璃面板
<span class="zh">气质</span>: 克制、编辑感、不 SaaS 风
<span class="kw">VERIFY</span>: 列出你改动的 3 个文件</pre>
        </aside>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="gs-section-head">
          <h2>三条咒语法则</h2>
          <p>酷，是因为可验证；帅，是因为仍属于 Miragea 的信号宇宙。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gs-grid3">
          <article class="gs-card">
            <div class="gs-kicker">◈ 01 · 制</div>
            <h3>约束即魔法</h3>
            <p>魔咒不是越长越好。输出格式、边界、验收标准——让 AI 在轨道上施法。</p>
          </article>
          <article class="gs-card">
            <div class="gs-kicker">◇ 02 · 咒</div>
            <h3>双语分工</h3>
            <p>英文写技术规格，中文写审美与语境。Codex 与中文生态各取所长。</p>
          </article>
          <article class="gs-card">
            <div class="gs-kicker">⬡ 03 · 证</div>
            <h3>可复现才算数</h3>
            <p>每集附咒语模板与检查清单。Example 路线：看得见、学得会、做得出。</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="gs-ep-list" aria-label="系列节目">
        <div class="gs-section-head" style="margin-bottom:0">
          <h2>魔咒系列</h2>
          <p>科普动画 + 口播 · B站更新</p>
        </div>
        <article class="gs-ep">
          <span class="gs-ep-num">EP01</span>
          <div>
            <h4>Codex 写代码，该用中文还是英文？</h4>
            <p>英中分工 · 强弱指令对比 · 固定 Prompt 模板</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/zh/geekspell/ep01-codex-language/">打开本集 →</a>
        </article>
        <article class="gs-ep">
          <span class="gs-ep-num">EP02</span>
          <div>
            <h4>榨干 Grok 4.5：强在哪？怎么用？</h4>
            <p>四个强项 · 五个习惯 · 高效开场模板</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/zh/geekspell/ep02-grok45/">打开本集 →</a>
        </article>
        <article class="gs-ep">
          <span class="gs-ep-num">EP03</span>
          <div>
            <h4>AI Agent 时代：不会被淘汰的人具备什么？</h4>
            <p>意图→可执行指令 · 定义问题 · 拆解 · 验证 · 长文+动画</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/zh/geekspell/ep03-agent-command/">打开本集 →</a>
        </article>
        <article class="gs-ep">
          <span class="gs-ep-num">EP04</span>
          <div>
            <h4>别再说「全部帮我做完」</h4>
            <p>范围切割 · 一块=目标+交付+验收</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/zh/geekspell/ep04-scope-split/">打开本集 →</a>
        </article>
        <article class="gs-ep">
          <span class="gs-ep-num">EP05</span>
          <div>
            <h4>验收回环（准备中）</h4>
            <p>检查点 · 完成定义 · 回滚 — EP04 与 EP06 之间的桥</p>
          </div>
          <span class="gs-ep-soon">Step by step 续更</span>
        </article>
        <article class="gs-ep">
          <span class="gs-ep-num">EP06</span>
          <div>
            <h4>一个人如何管理一支 Agent 团队</h4>
            <p>七种分工 · 八道监督 · 可验证的工作系统</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/zh/geekspell/ep06-agent-team/">打开本集 →</a>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="gs-lineage">
        <h3>Miragea 血统</h3>
        <p class="gs-lineage-copy">
          极客魔咒不是独立网红品牌，而是感知档案的执行层科普出口。源头在 Miragea，系统在 Eliora，播放在工坊。
        </p>
        <div class="gs-flow">
          <span>Miragea 档案</span>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
          <span>EX Example / Execution</span>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
          <span>宇宙 AI 工坊 ZH</span>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
          <span>B站 · 极客魔咒</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer class="gs-foot">
        极客魔咒工作室 · GeekSpell Studio · 与 AI 同行的魔法与咒语
        ·
        <a href="https://space.bilibili.com/1321407655" target="_blank" rel="noopener">space.bilibili.com/1321407655</a>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  .gs-page {
    --obsidian: #0a0a0f;
    --indigo: #1a1a3e;
    --spell-gold: #c9a962;
    --signal-cyan: #5b9cff;
    --spell-violet: #8b5cf6;
    --text: #e8ecf8;
    --muted: rgba(200, 208, 224, 0.65);
    --panel: rgba(10, 12, 22, 0.72);
    min-height: 100vh;
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', 'Noto Sans SC', system-ui, sans-serif;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 100% 60% at 50% -10%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.18) 0%, transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 80% 20%, rgba(91, 156, 255, 0.12) 0%, transparent 50%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--indigo) 0%, var(--obsidian) 45%, #050508 100%);
  }
  .gs-stars {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
    opacity: 0.45;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 12% 18%, #fff, transparent),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 72% 32%, #fff, transparent),
      radial-gradient(1.5px 1.5px at 48% 68%, #c9d4ff, transparent);
  }
  .gs-wrap {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1120px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 5.5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
  }
  .gs-topbar {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .gs-topbar a {
    color: var(--spell-gold);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .gs-topbar a:hover {
    color: #f0d9a0;
  }
  .gs-hero {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .gs-hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
      align-items: end;
    }
  }
  .gs-eyebrow {
    font-family: ui-monospace, 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--signal-cyan);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .gs-hero h1 {
    font-family: Georgia, 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 3.6rem);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .gs-hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--spell-gold);
  }
  .gs-sub-en {
    font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--spell-violet);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .gs-lead {
    max-width: 36rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
  .gs-tag {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    border-left: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.5);
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(232, 236, 248, 0.85);
  }
  .gs-cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .gs-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 2.75rem;
    padding: 0 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .gs-btn-primary {
    background: #f5f5f4;
    color: #0a0a0f;
  }
  .gs-btn-primary:hover {
    background: #fecdd3;
  }
  .gs-btn-ghost {
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .gs-btn-ghost:hover {
    border-color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
  }
  .gs-panel {
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.28);
    background: var(--panel);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .gs-panel-label {
    font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--spell-gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .gs-spell {
    font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #b8c8e8;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    word-break: break-word;
  }
  .gs-spell .kw {
    color: var(--signal-cyan);
  }
  .gs-spell .cm {
    color: rgba(200, 208, 224, 0.4);
  }
  .gs-spell .zh {
    color: #ffd166;
  }
  .gs-section-head {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .gs-section-head h2 {
    font-family: Georgia, 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
  }
  .gs-section-head p {
    max-width: 28rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .gs-grid3 {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .gs-grid3 {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
  .gs-card {
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }
  .gs-kicker {
    font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    color: #a5f3fc;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .gs-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .gs-card p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .gs-ep-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .gs-ep {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.2);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .gs-ep {
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
  .gs-ep-num {
    font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--spell-gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }
  .gs-ep h4 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .gs-ep p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .gs-ep a {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #fecdd3;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .gs-lineage {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(26, 26, 62, 0.6), rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.8));
  }
  .gs-lineage h3 {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .gs-lineage-copy {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 40rem;
  }
  .gs-flow {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem 1rem;
    font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .gs-flow .arrow {
    color: var(--spell-violet);
  }
  .gs-foot {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(200, 208, 224, 0.4);
  }
  .gs-foot a {
    color: var(--spell-gold);
  }
</style>
